tourBios.curYrHigh: While waiting for PGA TOUR Canada's season to begin, traveled to China and made his PGA TOUR China Series debut. Finished T59 at the Mission Hills Haikou Open. Shot rounds of 73-71-72-75 at the Sandbelt Trails Course to tie with Yi Cao, Hoon Heui Lee, Eric Mina and Wen Yi Huang.
tourBios.carHigh:
2013: In seven PGA TOUR Canada starts, failed to make a cut.
 
2012: Rebounded from a first-round 80, with rounds of 68-70-71 to earn exempt status at the Fall Qualifying School...Made the cut in his first and last tournaments of the PGA TOUR Canada season. Was T21 at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open and T43 at The Great Waterway Classic.
 
2011: Made two cuts in 10 PGA TOUR Canada starts. Cuts came in back-to-back starts—at T64 at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open and a T32 at the Western Championship...Received PGA TOUR Canada conditional status after finishing T20 at the California Winter Qualifying School...Also played on the All-American Tour
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Was a winner at the 2010 Arizona Mid-Amateur and the MAIA Classic. Won the 2008 Vancouver Amateur. , 2-time All- American

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T21st in 2012 at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T99th in Par 3 Performance on the PGA TOUR Canada.
